<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="541" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1405,1647]" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1477,1504]" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">Distribution</emphasis>
. This species was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[745,807,1477,1503]" name="Israel" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">Israel</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[825,894,1477,1504]" country="Israel" name="Haifa" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">Haifa</collectingRegion>
). Its presence in 
<collectingCountry box="[1090,1149,1477,1503]" name="Syria" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">Syria</collectingCountry>
was reported by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bezdek, A." pageId="5" pageNumber="541" pagination="249 - 280" refId="ref6643" refString="Bezdek, A. (2016) Rhizotrogini. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Volume 3. Scarabaeoidea, Scirtoidea, Dascilloidea, Buprestoidea, Byrrhoidea. Revised and updated edition. Brill, Leiden, Boston, pp. 249 - 280." type="book chapter" year="2016">Bezděk (2016)</bibRefCitation>
and is here confirmed. We record it here also for 
<collectingCountry box="[781,879,1513,1539]" name="Lebanon" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">Lebanon</collectingCountry>
(
<emphasis bold="true" box="[896,1132,1513,1540]" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">first country record</emphasis>
, 
<figureCitation box="[1145,1214,1513,1539]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="10.[151,250,2018,2043]" captionTargetBox="[234,1349,458,1988]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[220,1367,445,1998]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURE 4. Distribution map of Haplidia Hope species in Lebanon." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3602754" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3602754/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="541" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1405,1647]" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1550,1576]" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">Remarks.</emphasis>
The three species 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Chikatunov &amp; Pavlicek" authorityYear="1997" box="[526,642,1550,1575]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Aplidia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="joannis">
<emphasis box="[526,642,1550,1575]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">H. joannis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Montreuil" authorityYear="2005" box="[657,773,1549,1575]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="indaryi">
<emphasis box="[657,773,1549,1575]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">H. indaryi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Chikatunov &amp; Pavlicek" authorityYear="1997" box="[829,968,1550,1575]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Aplidia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="petrovitzi">
<emphasis box="[829,968,1550,1575]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="541">H. petrovitzi</emphasis>
